                        <interp inst="t18401019-name-225" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM KINNER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I got this certificate of the prisoner's former conviction from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—I was a witness in the case—the prisoner is the person who was then tried and convicted.</p>
